snippet.title: Hello Neighbor Steals Our Toys and Locks Us Out of Our House!!!
snippet.description:
Hello Neighbor in Real Life Steals Our Toys and Locks Us Out of Our House!!!
Subscribe to Madison and Beyond: http://tinyurl.com/madisonsub
Subscribe to Trinity and Beyond: http://tinyurl.com/trinitysub
Check out our New Video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uLVjUV0NT38&list=PLH2I3pcDbffEVSMcjBSVzxmw_s_-zBrnE

Real Life Hello Neighbor Steals Our Suitcase Full of Toy Fair Toys and Locks Us Out of Our Own Home!! We are back from our trip to the New York toy fair and we brought home a suitcase full of some of the newest toys that are coming out! Trinity and Madison went to open the suitcase only to find that some of the toys were missing! That could mean only one thing, Hello Neighbor took our new toys. There were so many of them hidden throughout the house but we managed to find them all! Of course it wasn't easy. Hello Neighbor kept coming after us and catching us. We had to put an end to it and kick him out once and for all!
